Uses of Package
net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo.datatypes

  • Packages that use net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo.datatypes 
    Package Description
    net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo
    Provides the classes for parsing the output of various olsrd plugins.
    net.commotionwireless.olsrinfo.datatypes
    Provides the classes for the Jackson JSON parser to fill using the data parsed from the JSON data dump from olsrd's jsoninfo plugin.
